          "body": {
            "text": "A small overhanging crag with some fine routes. Situated in dark coniferous woodland – don't forget insect repellent!",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:margreteberg"
            ]
          }
        },
        "vagbeskrivning": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Directions",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:margreteberg"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "Take Route 222, Värmdöleden, and exit towards Orminge. After Orminge C, turn left onto Skarpövägen, then take the first right onto Hasseluddsvägen. After 200 m, turn right onto Margretebergsvägen. Follow the gravel road to a turning area. Park and walk back along the road. The crag is on the left, in the woods opposite the red houses, and can be glimpsed from the gravel road.\n\nAfter climbing, a visit to Restaurang Telegraf is recommended (http://www.alltomstockholm.se/profil.aspx?fid=2&EntityID=898707)",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:margreteberg"
            ]
          }
        },
